  "transcript": [
    {
      "turn": 1,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Hi Aarti, I’ve been thinking about how you linked nephron functions with clinical examples , that was a solid win. How did your endocrinology study go?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Not good. Too tired. Hormones confuse me. I’ll try again."
    },
    {
      "turn": 2,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Got it, hormones are tricky, even for experts. What part feels the heaviest right now?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The insulin and glucagon part. How they balance blood sugar… it all blurs. Need to make notes. Maybe diagrams. Kya karun?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 3,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Insulin and glucagon are tough — even small details matter. Try sketching their roles in simple steps. What’s the first thing that confuses you?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The feedback loop — like how the body knows to release one or the other. Also, the liver’s role… feels like there are too many steps. Bored."
    },
    {
      "turn": 4,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The body’s signals are subtle, and the liver adds more layers, it’s a lot. Focus on one step at a time. What part would you start with?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "The liver part. It’s too many steps. Can’t focus. Need tea."
    },
    {
      "turn": 5,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "The liver does have many steps, that’s why diagrams help. Tea can help too. What kind do you like?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Green tea. Helps me stay awake. But today, even that’s not working. Kahi vada pav kahi coffee?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 6,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Green tea is a good pick, but even that won’t help if your mind’s heavy. A quick vada pav and coffee break sounds like a plan. What’s next after that?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Read notes for 20 mins. Then try insulin diagram. Maybe. But coffee first. Ja rahi hoon."
    },
    {
      "turn": 7,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "You’ll feel better after that coffee , and the diagram will wait for you. Tell me, what’s on your mind while you’re out?"
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "user",
      "content": "Just the notes and the diagram. Also, if I’ll remember anything. Coffee first, then fight with hormones. Boring. Ja rahi hoon."
    },
    {
      "turn": 8,
      "role": "maya",
      "content": "Right, coffee first, then you'll tackle that hormone maze. What's the one thing you want to remember most?"
    }
  ],
